Here, `i` is the **index**, not the _value_ at that index. Also, your loop&#39;s condition is wrong. It&#39;s already exclusive, since you are using `&lt;`, meaning you should not be subtracting one from the size of the list.

You want something like:

    private static int findSmallest(ArrayList&lt;Integer&gt; list){
        int smallest = list.get(0);
        for (int i = 0; i &lt; list.size(); i++) {
            if (list.get(i) &lt; smallest) {
                smallest = list.get(i);
            }
        }
        return smallest;
    }

